==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: shăd'ō

===Noun===
'''shadow'''  (''plural:'' '''[[shadows]]''')

# A dark image projected onto a surface where light is blocked by an object.
# One who [[secretly]] or [[furtively]] [[follow]]s another.

